summary: A Racemenu Preset of Robin Torkar
descriptionHtml:
[size=4]

Installation[/size]

[size=3]Place the 0_Pixlpit.jslot  file in your Presets folder - G:\Steam\steamapps\common\skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets[/size]
[size=3]The Preset should now be available in the Racemenu Preset section under the name 0_Pixlpit
[color=#ffff00][size=4]Race is Breton[/size][/color][/size]
